    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<h2>Solen Mereth — Senior Clerk, Cindren &amp; Vhal Hardby</h2>\n<p><em>The compromised senior clerk of the Hardby branch. Late sixties, not corrupt by inclination but pressured into compliance for nearly three years. Yields under proper procedural pressure; will not survive the trial that follows.</em></p>\n<h3>Description</h3>\n<p>Late sixties. Hardby-born, white hair carefully combed, narrow gold-rimmed reading lenses, dark broadcloth coat with a small enamel firm-pin at the lapel. Long pale hands stained with ink. Stiff knees. Walks short distances only.</p>\n<h3>Combat behavior</h3>\n<p><strong>Will not fight.</strong> Yields immediately to any threat of violence. He has no combat training and is in poor health.</p>\n<h3>Statblock summary (CR 0, PB +2)</h3>\n<p><strong>AC</strong> 10 · <strong>HP</strong> 14 (4d6) · <strong>Speed</strong> 25 ft. · <strong>Init</strong> +0 · <strong>Passive Perception</strong> 12</p>\n<p><strong>STR</strong> 9 (-1) · <strong>DEX</strong> 10 (+0) · <strong>CON</strong> 10 (+0) · <strong>INT</strong> 16 (+3) · <strong>WIS</strong> 14 (+2) · <strong>CHA</strong> 12 (+1)</p>\n<p><strong>Saves:</strong> INT +5, WIS +4. <strong>Skills:</strong> History +5, Insight +4, Investigation +5, Persuasion +3.</p>\n<p><strong>Senses:</strong> Passive Perception 12. <strong>Languages:</strong> Common, Old Aerdi.</p>\n<h3>Source</h3>\n<p><em>Blooming Rot, Part 2 — Phase 3.</em> See <em>Cindren &amp; Vhal Hardby Branch → Solen Mereth — Compromised Senior Clerk</em> for full profile, the three approach paths, and the Aerdi commercial subpoena procedure.</p>",
        "public": ""
      },
